contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.communi.CommunityGroupContentDescription:
The Milwaukee Kentico User Group (MKE KUG) brings users, developers, designers, marketers, and strategists together to collaborate, learn, share, and network on all things related to the Kentico ecosystem.

We seek to support and provide guidance from and for the community and to engage sponsors and Kentico channel partner representatives in collaborative learning and networking.

This group is operated with direct support from Kentico regional partners.
